    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "The Anaphothrips genus-group of Thripidae (Thysanoptera) from Saudi Arabia with two new species of Eremiothrips" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529882>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529894>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529896>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529898> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529882>
    dc:description "Figures 1–6. Antennae: (1) Aptinothrips rufus (Haliday); (2–6) Eremiothrips Priesner: (2) E. aldryhimi sp. nov., (3) E. arya (zur Strassen), (4) E. efflatouni (Priesner), (5) E. similis Bhatti, (6) E. unicolour sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5529882/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529894>
    dc:description "Figures 22–31. Eremiothrips species. Male tergite IX: (22) E. aldryhimi sp. nov., (23) E. arya (zur Strassen), (24) E. efflatouni (Priesner), (25) E. similis Bhatti, (26) E. unicolour sp. nov. Male sternites III–VII: (27) E. aldryhimi sp. nov., (28) E. arya (zur Strassen), (29) E. efflatouni (Priesner), (30) E. similis Bhatti, (31) E. unicolour sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5529894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529896>
    dc:description "Figures 32–37. Eremiothrips species. Head and pronotum: (32) E. aldryhimi sp. nov., (33) E. efflatouni (Priesner), (34) E. similis Bhatti, (35) E. unicolour sp. nov. Mouth cones: (36) E. aldryhimi sp. nov., (37) E. unicolour sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5529896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5529898>
    dc:description "Figures 38–45. Eremiothrips species. E. aldryhimi sp. nov.: (38) female, (39) male. (40) E. efflatouni (Priesner). E. similis Bhatti: macropterous (41) female, (42) male; (43) micropterous male. E. unicolour sp. nov.: (44) female, (45) male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5529898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

